---
import { createT } from '../i18n/translations';
export interface Props { lang?: string; }
const { lang = 'zh' } = Astro.props;
const _ = createT(lang);
const isEn = lang === 'en';
---
<section id="mcp" class="relative py-32 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-surface-03 border border-surface-06 mb-10">
        <span class="text-sm text-brand-gold font-medium">{_('mcp.badge')}</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">
        {_('mcp.title.1')}<span class="gradient-text">{_('mcp.title.2')}</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        {_('mcp.subtitle')}
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
      <!-- Store Memory -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-bg-card border border-surface-06">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-gold mb-6">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="3" y2="15"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">{isEn ? 'Memory Writing (store_memory)' : '记忆写入（store_memory）'}</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
          {isEn ? <>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> AI tools auto-save high-value conversation info to your memory bank</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> record_time: ISO 8601 format (e.g. 2025-07-10T14:30:00+08:00)</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> title: up to 50 characters; content: up to 10,000 characters</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> memory-digest: AI summarizes chat logs (Kimi, ChatGPT, etc.) into local drafts</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> memory-sync: auto batch-upload drafts daily; drafts kept 30 days offline, auto-retry on reconnect</li>
          </> : <>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> 接入 AI 工具后，自动将对话中的高价值信息保存至个人记忆库</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> record_time：事件时间，ISO 8601 格式（如 2025-07-10T14:30:00+08:00）</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> title：最大 50 字；content：最大 10000 字</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> memory-digest：AI 自动汇总聊天记录，提炼核心结论，生成本地草稿</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> memory-sync：每日凌晨批量上报草稿；断网留存 30 天，恢复后自动补传</li>
          </>}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Query Memories -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-bg-card border border-surface-06">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-gold mb-6">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-4">{isEn ? 'Memory Reading (query_memories)' : '记忆读取（query_memories）'}</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
          {isEn ? <>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> AI tools can freely query all memory data: manual entries, auto diaries, location trails</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> start_date / end_date: YYYY-MM-DD format; defaults to last 90 days</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> limit: up to 500 results (default), max 1000</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> Results sorted by time descending, grouped by date with time, title, location, and full content</li>
          </> : <>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> 接入的 AI 工具可自由检索全部记忆数据，含手动记录、自动日记、位置轨迹</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> start_date / end_date：YYYY-MM-DD 格式，未传参默认查询最近 90 天</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> limit：返回条数上限，默认 500 条，最大 1000 条</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold shrink-0">-</span> 查询结果按时间倒序、按日期分组，包含时间、标题、位置、完整内容</li>
          </>}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Security -->
    <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-bg-card border border-surface-06">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-gold">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">{isEn ? 'Security & Access Control' : '安全与权限控制'}</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-sm">
        {isEn ? <>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-surface-02"><span class="text-brand-gold font-medium">One-click Key</span><p class="text-text-secondary mt-1">Generate, rotate, or delete API Keys in the Mini Program settings</p></div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-surface-02"><span class="text-brand-gold font-medium">Rate Limiting</span><p class="text-text-secondary mt-1">30 req/min per API Key to prevent abuse</p></div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-surface-02"><span class="text-brand-gold font-medium">30-min Cache</span><p class="text-text-secondary mt-1">Query results cached for 30 minutes for faster access</p></div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-surface-02"><span class="text-brand-gold font-medium">Data Isolation</span><p class="text-text-secondary mt-1">Switching to custom backend creates a completely separate data space</p></div>
        </> : <>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-surface-02"><span class="text-brand-gold font-medium">一键生成</span><p class="text-text-secondary mt-1">小程序设置页一键生成、轮换或删除 API Key</p></div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-surface-02"><span class="text-brand-gold font-medium">独立限流</span><p class="text-text-secondary mt-1">每个 API Key 限制 30 次/分钟</p></div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-surface-02"><span class="text-brand-gold font-medium">30 分钟缓存</span><p class="text-text-secondary mt-1">查询结果自带缓存提升访问速度</p></div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-surface-02"><span class="text-brand-gold font-medium">数据隔离</span><p class="text-text-secondary mt-1">切换自定义后端后数据完全独立，互不干扰</p></div>
        </>}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
